Ignacio ANGUIANO, Appellant, v. W. W. KNOPP, Immigration Inspector, Appellee. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. November 20, 1929. Rehearing Denied December 14, 1929. No. 5668. Howell J. Mueller, of San Antonio, Tex. (Hirshberg, Stone & Mueller and Howell J. Mueller, all of San Antonio, Tex., on the brief), for appellant. John D. Hartman, U. S. Atty., of San Antonio, Tex., for appellee.

Before WALKER, BRYAN, and FOSTER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment is affirmed.
